page.title: 07PETS
page.content: I HAVE GOT 12 RABBITS AT HOME.2 ARE LIGHT BROWN.5 ARE BLACK.2 ARE GREY AND 3 ARE WHITE.EVERY NIGHT I HAVE TO PUT THEM IN THEIR BOX AND IN THE MORNING I HAVE TO LET THEM OUT.AT DINNER TIME I HAVE TO FEED THEM.I FEED THEM ON LETTUCE AND CARROTS AND DANDELIONS. GOLD FISH ARE A SORT OF A GOLD.AND THEY EAT A KIND OF THIN SAWDUST BUT COLOURED.I KEEP SOME GOLD FISH BUT WE HAVE ONLY 2 ONE IS MY SISTER'S AND I HAVE GOT THE OTHER GOLD FISH.MY GRANDAD HAS LOTS OF DOGS AND THEY ARE SPANIELS.AND THEY KEEP HAVING PUPPIES. SO HE SELLS THEM IF PEOPLE COME TO HIS HOUSE.SOME TIMES I HAVE TO HELP HIM MIX UP THE FOOD BUT FOR THE PUPPIES YOU HAVE TO GIVE THEM WARM MILK.
